business and manage and develop our people to ensure every employee is given the opportunity to achieve their potential.    Signed by:                                                                                                   David Connell  HR Director  Vauxhall UK    2nd March 2018             DOWNLOAD THE GENDER PAY GAP REPORT FOR VAUXHALL UK       VISIT THE GOVERNMENT GENDER PAY GAP REPORTING PAGE               Quote       Personalise       Test Drive       Calculate       Brochure       Stock Locator        VEHICLES     City Cars    Small Cars    Family Cars    7 Seater Cars    SUVs    Hatchback Cars    Estate Cars    Vans         Help Me Choose    VXR       USEFUL TOOLS     Stock Locator    Finance Calculator    Find a Retailer    Personalise         Book a Test Drive    Request a Quote    Value My Vehicle    Request a Brochure    Book a Service    Newsletter       EXPERIENCE     OnStar    Infotainment    ecoTEC         News & Events    Vauxhall Football    V-Mag       ABOUT     About Vauxhall    Customer Excellence    Awards & Accolades    The Environment    Contact Us    How we use your Data         Find us on                          © 2018 Vauxhall Motors Limited      WLTP      AdBlue      Modern Slavery Act      Privacy Policy      Cookie Policy      Accessibility      Vauxhall UK Tax Strategy      Gender Pay Gap                                      Questions? powered by velaro live chat              